_sText: Gg_bathroom by BrainFart aka Flanders (ned so grob)
Keep your game clean at the Bathhouse.

Im proud of this project and getting a lot of great feedback from others. 
I wanted to add so much more but i couldnt cause i maxed out the max_planes. I just couldnt fit anymore in there. Well, my passion for interior remodeling inspired this  messy remodel. Ive seen many rat maps out there that are finished nice bathrooms but never one under construction. Its pretty medium sized and great for gungame believe it or not. I will be making this a de_map but first I want to get this out there as a gg for navigation and bombsite locations. This map is best played with a server script that randomly places the player_spawns but the map originaly has 12cts on the wet saw and window side and 12 t's by the craftsman tool box and contractors binder. every texture, tool, product, shape or any thing is originaly designed and created custom by me. uhhhh, credit Valve for the wall and hardibacker looking texture and thats it. the rest is me. lots of work. 6 full days on this. 6am-1am everyday!

This map is custom created by me, shotgun_master it is free to distribute. Enjoy it and and do NOT claim it as your own work! Them map consists of 20 spawn points, 10 for terrorsists and 10 for counter terrorists. Each team spawn location is located on opposites sides of the map. In the middle of the map is a maze of boxes, and on opposites sides of the map is a ramp (one on each side, total of two). There is a catwalk coming off the two ramps, through the middle of the map.

Well, I think I did pretty well this this, it being my first map and all.
It's been a hit on my clans Gungame server.. and everyone who played it has said it's a fun map.

The Wire Ramp in the middle (or the "Rage Cage", as I call it) has 3 breakable entrances, and on my server I like to play knife only in it. Just a Suggestion.

Also, the maze upstairs has lights that slowly change from dark to light. Perfect for knifing :D

Special thanks to ۩₣ﻆ۩Lectric.Smooth and BPL for the version 2 ideas.

This is a Gun Game map with 32 spawn points. There are no Buyzones.

This map is very quick for gameplay, yet it also has a few decent camp spots for those of you that are scared of combat. It is excellent for gungame as there are scenarios within the map that are well suited for every gun in CS (decent snipe/camp areas, decent run n' gun areas, etc.). 

The only real difference between this map and the original Bad Neighbors map is that I've opened up the houses. (This was by popular demand.)

Enjoy!

This is a Gun Game map made for up to 28 people, ideally for 24 people and 4 extra spawnpoints to avoid people spawning on top of one another. Also there are no Buyzones.

This map is very quick for gameplay and is excellent for gungame as there are many areas for knifing and close combat.
